Requirements
====================================================

* Virtualbox
* Vagrant (>1.1.x)

Installation
====================================================

git clone git@git.niekom.de:datenbetrieb/infrastructure.git
cd infrastructure

Usage
====================================================

vagrant up


<------------------------->
<-- for developing only -->
<------------------------->


Manage Machine Definitions (veewee)
====================================================

https://github.com/datenbetrieb/veewee

veewee gem must be installed from source (>=0.3.8.dev)


- export PROVIDER=vbox
- veewee $PROVIDER build
- veewee $PROVIDER export
- mv XX.box boxes/.
- scp boxes/XX.box h01n:/srv/www/boxes.datenbetrieb.de/.
